{
  "stem": "15197.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Leshner ?] Street and it was about-- after 4 o'clock-- and a Jewish policeman came to his family telling them that they heard on the Jewish police station that this street is going to be blocked and deported.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we waited all day long together with the family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was in a separate place, and by 5:00 when everybody gave up-- nothing took place, nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mother and my brother went up to prepare something to eat-- --and at that moment when they went up, the street was blocked and deportations started, selections started.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I couldn't see them because the street was full of people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I couldn't see not my brother, I couldn't go up to them anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I at that time was having just a piece of paper to show that I am working in a German workshop, [INAUDIBLE] workshops.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I gave it to the German, he looked at me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I showed him the paper, he looked again at me, and sent me to the right.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was young at that time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When I was on the right side for the people-- I didn't know even if this is the right, if it is-- but it was the right side.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The selection was still going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I didn't see my brother and I didn't see my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My sister was with her workshop in the kitchen, with the staff.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I was looking for them and suddenly, I heard when the van was passing by calling my name.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I want to go to where the voice is coming from, but I was separated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They cut me off, they didn't let me go to move away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were taken away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I didn't see them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I just-- in my mind I just heard the voice.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
